<div class="why-page">

  <p class="why-eyebrow">SINISTER STASH</p>

  <h1 class="why-title">Shipping & Returns</h1>

  <div class="why-divider"></div>

  <div class="why-section">
    <h2 class="why-heading">Shipping</h2>
    <p>We ship internationally for most products. That includes apparel, stickers, patches, and non-accessory goods. Items classified as firearm accessories are limited to the United States only due to export regulations. If a product is US-only, it'll be noted on the product page.</p>
    <p><strong>Free shipping</strong> on all orders over $50.</p>
    <p>Most orders ship within 3–5 business days. Apparel and patches ship via USPS. You'll get a tracking number by email once your order ships.</p>
    <p>Custom or made-to-order items may take a bit longer. We'll note estimated timelines on those product pages.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="why-section">
    <h2 class="why-heading">Returns</h2>
    <p>We stand behind what we make. If something's not right, here's how it works:</p>
    <ul class="why-resource-list">
      <li><strong>Standard items</strong> (stickers, patches, non-customized apparel) are returnable within 30 days. Must be unworn, unwashed, and in original condition.</li>
      <li><strong>Custom or personalized items</strong> are final sale. We can't resell something made specifically for you.</li>
      <li><strong>Defective or damaged items</strong>: contact us immediately and we'll make it right. Send a photo and we'll get a replacement or refund sorted fast.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="why-section">
    <h2 class="why-heading">How to start a return</h2>
    <p>Email us through our <a href="/pages/contact">Contact</a> page with your order number and what's going on. We'll respond within 1–2 business days with return instructions.</p>
    <p>Refunds are processed within 5–7 business days after we receive the returned item. Original shipping costs are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="why-section">
    <h2 class="why-heading">Exchanges</h2>
    <p>Need a different size? Start a return and place a new order. It's the fastest way to get the right thing to you. If you use the same discount code and it's expired, hit us up and we'll sort it out.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="why-closing">
    <p>Questions about an order? <a href="/pages/contact" style="color: #F0645A; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;">Get in touch.</a></p>
  </div>

</div>

